dn't%20work%20well%2C%20%26quot%3Bjust%20in%20case%26quot%3B%20I%20ever%20needed%20them%20%E2%80%94%20as%20if%20I'd%20never%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20a%20new%20spatula%20or%20bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20without%20extra%20stuff%20is%20habit-forming.%20My%20kitchen%20remains%20functional%20and%20uncluttered.%20But%20poverty%20mindset%20persists%20upstairs%20in%20my%20cluttered%20bedroom.%20I%20know%20the%20only%20cure%20is%20to%20pare%20down%20one%20category%20of%20stuff%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDecluttering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fhow-to-save-money%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaves%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20makes%20it%20easier%20not%20to%20buy%20the%20next%20shiny%20object.%20I%20guard%20my%20open%20space%20jealously%20and%20am%20more%20selective%20about%20what%20I%20bring%20home.%20There's%20no%20room%20for%20stowaways%20and%20freeloaders%3B%20every%20item%20must%20have%20a%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22138cbc53-02c7-496c-9cdd-56812db25ae3%5C%22%3ELearning%20to%20love%20having%20less%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20sister-in-law%2C%20the%20minimalist%2C%20is%20my%20decluttering%20guru.%20But%20when%20she%20told%20me%20I%20needed%20to%20own%20less%20clothing%2C%20I%20said%20no%20way.%20I%20love%20clothes.%20I%20love%20clothes%20shopping.%20Assembling%20the%20right%20outfit%20to%20wear%20in%20the%20morning%20is%20my%20happy%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20so%20many%20clothes%20hanging%20in%20my%20closet%20that%20everything%20was%20stuffed%20so%20tight%20it%20got%20instantly%20wrinkled.%20And%20yes%2C%20my%20dresser%20drawers%20were%20packed%20to%20the%20gills.%20So%20%E2%80%94%20I%20gave%20in%20and%20started%20paring%20down%20my%20wardrobe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20shed%20clothing%2C%20I%20realized%20my%20closet%20was%20filled%20with%20guilt.%20I%20felt%20terrible%20about%20the%20shirt%20I%20wore%20all%20the%20time%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20which%20now%20sits%20neglected%20on%20a%20hanger.%20Giving%20myself%20permission%20to%20pass%20on%20clothing%20that%20no%20longer%20speaks%20to%20me%2C%20even%20if%20I%20once%20loved%20it%2C%20frees%20me%20to%20appreciate%20and%20enjoy%20the%20clothes%20I%20want%20to%20wear%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20surprising%2C%20getting%20rid%20of%20clothes%20has%20broken%20my%20clothes-shopping%20addiction.%20I%20don't%20want%20the%20newest%20dress%20from%20a%20designer%20I%20like%20or%20the%20latest%20collaboration%20between%20brands%20I%20follow.%20I'm%20happy%20with%20the%20manageable%20amount%20of%20clothing%20I%20have%2C%20and%20I%20like%20how%20I%20feel%20when%20my%20closet%20is%20lighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20when%20I%20have%20too%20much%20stuff%2C%20I%20buy%20multiples%20of%20the%20same%20thing%3A%20The%20new%20black%20dress%20I%20can't%20live%20without%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20old%20black%20dress%20squished%20into%20the%20back%20of%20my%20closet.%20Now%2C%20when%20I%20think%20about%20purchasing%20new%20clothing%2C%20I%20ask%20myself%20if%20I%20already%20have%20something%20like%20it.%20Do%20I%20really%20need%20it%3F%20Do%20I%20really%20want%20it%3F%20And%20the%20answer%20is%20usually%20no%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20great%20for%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-budgeting-apps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230e20659-ab2a-4b55-8d5b-c9e45b3eaa48%5C%22%3EMy%20home%20is%20not%20a%20waste%20receptacle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fasked-tax-attorney-what-know-about-moving-new-country-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMy%20anxiety%20since%20the%20election%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20added%20new%20urgency%20to%20downsizing%3A%20%3Cem%3EIf%20I%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20country%2C%20would%20I%20take%20this%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20For%2090%25%20of%20my%20possessions%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20