ve%20with%20John%20Mulaney.%26quot%3B%20This%20follows%20the%20six-week%20%26quot%3BJohn%20Mulaney's%20Everybody's%20in%20LA%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20projects%20Mulaney%20has%20had%20with%20the%20streamer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effort%20to%20sign%20podcasters%2C%20however%2C%20is%20an%20indication%20of%20Netflix's%20general%20warming%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20working%20with%20creators%2C%20industry%20insiders%20told%20BI.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20Netflix%20has%20welcomed%20YouTube-born%20creators%2C%20including%20entertainers%20The%20Sidemen%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fms-rachel-netflix-streaming-1236273967%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekids'%20educator%20Ms.%20Rachel%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideo%20podcasts%20could%20be%20a%20natural%20extension%20of%20that%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20see%20a%20world%20in%20which%20audio-only%20and%20vodcasts%20are%20streamed%20on%20Netflix%20so%20that%20they%20can%20offer%20an%20all-in-one%20place%20to%20keep%20users%20on%20their%20platform%20for%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jessica%20Cordova%20Kramer%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Lemonada%20Media%2C%20which%20works%20with%20Julia%20Louis%20Dreyfuss%20and%20Meghan%20Markle%20on%20their%20podcasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideo%20podcasts%20can%20appeal%20to%20Netflix%20and%20other%20streamers%20because%20they%20are%20cheaper%20than%20traditional%20TV%20shows%2C%20their%20regular%20release%20schedules%20can%20build%20a%20habit%2C%20and%20they%20can%20help%20boost%20ad%20revenue%20by%20adding%20additional%20inventory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20have%20spoken%20with%20multiple%20streamers%20looking%20to%20partner%20with%20us%20for%20licensed%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20Cordova%20Kramer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247f1a088-2d82-448e-8384-d4d4df8a3dda%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPodcasts%20are%20increasingly%20being%20watched%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20is%20no%20doubt%20seeing%20how%20YouTube%20has%20become%20the%20top%20platform%20for%20podcasts.%20It%20beat%20out%20Spotify%20and%20Apple%20as%20of%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edisonresearch.com%2Fyoutube-is-the-preferred-podcast-listening-service%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEdison%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Creators%20like%20Tana%20Mongeau%20and%20Logan%20Paul%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20are%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-are-using-podcasts-to-reinvent-themselves-earn-more-money-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echasing%20the%20podcast%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20creating%20their%20own%20shows%2C%20helping%20expand%20their%20business%20through%20touring%2C%20merch%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20podcasts%2C%20especially%20those%20of%20the%20talk%20variety%2C%20also%20now%20have%20video%20components.%20Edison%20found%20that%2089%25%20of%20weekly%20Gen-Z%20podcast%20listeners%20watched%20(or%20listened%20to)%20podcasts%20with%20video%20as%20of%20the%20end%20of%202024.%20YouTube%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.youtube%2Fnews-and-events%2F2024-recap-of-youtube-on-tv%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20people%20watched%20400%20million%20hours%20of%20podcasts%20on%20televisions%20in%202024%20via%20its%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20trend%20has%20drawn%20the%20format%20closer%20to%20the%20daytime%20and%20late-night%20talk%20shows%20that%20have%20been%20on%20TV%20for%20decades%2C%20said%20Vox%20Media's%20SVP%20and%20general%20manager%20for%20audio%20and%20digital%20video%20Ray%20Chao.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChao%20said%20that%20TV%20companies%20other%20than%20Netflix%20had%20already%20sought%20out%20talk%20shows%20that%20began%20in%20the%20digital%20realm.%20He%20pointed%20to%20Pat%20McAfee%20at%20ESPN%20and%20%26quot%3BHot%20Ones%26quot%3B%20at%20Hulu.%20Chao%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Vox%20Media's%20active%20business%20opportunities%20in%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223104%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smartless%20hosts%20Jason%20Bateman%2C%20Will%20Arnett%2C%20and%20Sean%20Hayes%20sitting%20on%20a%20white%20couch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67aa6a8deb4be2fff9a42c28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222070%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20SmartLess%20podcast%20%E2%80%94%20hosted%20by%20Jason%20Bateman%2C%20Will%20Arnett%2C%20and%20Sean%20Hayes%20%E2%80%94%20spawned%20a%20tour%20docuseries%20on%20Max.%3Cp%3ECindy%20Ord%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20SiriusXM%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20insiders%20say%20more%20streamers%20entering%20the%20fray%20could%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20the%20podcast%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPodcasting%20has%20sort%20of%20been%20through%20a%20lot%20the%20last%2018%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PAVE%20Studios%20founder%20Max%20Cutler%2C%20citing%20Apple's%20iOS%2017%20update%2C%20which%20changed%20podcast%20downloads%20and%20impacted%20ads.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20someone%20like%20Netflix%20come%20in%20will%20really%20help%20grow%20the%20overall%20pie%20of%20listenership%20and%20viewership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2fcec9b-3788-45f6-90a6-2bef2920a0bf%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20Netflix%20want%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20insiders%20said%20they%20see%20potential%20Netflix%20deals%20going%20a%20few%20ways.%20Netflix%20could%20license%20existing%20podcasts%20and%20forego%20exclusivity%2C%20as%20it%20did%20with%20%26quot%3BThe%20Amazing%20Digital%20Circus%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20popular%20YouTube%20show%20that%20came%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftudum%2Farticles%2Fthe-amazing-digital-circus-netflix-date-cast-details%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20in%20October%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20may%20also%20want%20to%20have%20something%20unique%2C%20three%20people%20f