to%20refund%20much%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20house%20as%20well%20as%20damages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20judge%20ordered%20a%20refund%20for%20a%20billionaire%20couple%20who%20paid%20%C2%A332.5%20million%20(about%20%2440%20million)%20for%20a%20mansion%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20moth%20infestation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20UK%20High%20Court%20judge%20ruled%20that%20Iya%20Patarkatsishvili%2C%20daughter%20of%20the%20Georgian%20billionaire%20tycoon%20Badri%20Patarkatsishvili%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20Yevhen%20Hunyak%2C%20can%20hand%20the%20home%20back%20to%20the%20seller%2C%20the%20property%20developer%20William%20Woodward-Fisher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatarkatsishvili%20and%20Hunyak%20purchased%20Horbury%20Villa%20in%20Notting%20Hill%2C%20west%20London%2C%20in%20May%202019.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPatarkatsishvili-and-another-v-Woodward-Fisher.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20judgment%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20within%20days%20of%20moving%20in%2C%20they%20started%20noticing%20moths%20flying%20around%20and%20landing%20on%20their%20cutlery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20found%20moths%20in%20clothes%2C%20wine%20glasses%2C%20and%20toothbrushes%20and%20swatted%20away%20hundreds%20a%20day%2C%20the%20judgment%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPest%20control%20companies%20found%20that%20insulation%20in%20the%20ceiling%20was%20the%20source%20of%20the%20issue.%20The%20works%20to%20replace%20the%20insulation%20cost%20%C2%A3270%2C000%2C%20the%20hearing%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20claimants%20accused%20Woodward-Fisher%20of%20knowingly%20selling%20the%20house%20with%20the%20moth%20infestation.%20He%20was%20found%20to%20have%20known%20about%20the%20issue%20since%20early%202018%20but%20failed%20to%20inform%20Patarkatsishvili%20and%20Hunyak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%