tive%20AI%20provider%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20startup's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20Appu%20Shaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMobius%20Labs'%20platform%20aims%20to%20reduce%20the%20energy%20required%20to%20run%20AI%20models%2C%20which%20is%20otherwise%20costly%20and%20energy-intensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20says%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bquantized%26quot%3B%20Meta's%20Llama70B%20model%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%2C%20divided%20it%20into%20smaller%2C%20more%20measurable%20increments%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20losing%20accuracy%2C%20and%20enabling%20it%20to%20run%20on%20a%20single%20GPU%20instead%20of%20four%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Riegler%2C%20whose%20VC%20firm%20has%20backed%20the%20company.%20%26quot%3BThis%20method%20skips%20unnecessary%20calculations%20without%20sacrificing%20the%20accuracy%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20output%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGemesys%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dennis%20Michaelis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6717cea99b3250dbbce92bf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22708%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDennis%20Michaelis%2C%20CEO%20of%20Gemesys.%3Cp%3EGemesys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20raised%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2412.8%20million%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackers%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Atlantic%20Labs%2C%20NRW.Bank%2C%20and%20Plug%20and%20Play%20Tech%20Center%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuggested%20by%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Andreas%20Riegler%2C%20founding%20partner%20at%20APEX%20Ventures%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20does%20and%20why%20it's%20one%20to%20watch%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20AI-hardware%20startup%20Gemesys%20has%20developed%20a%20chip%20that%20works%20similarly%20to%20the%20human%20brain%20and%20positions%20itself%20as%20a%20more%20energy-efficient%20alternative%20for%20AI%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202023%2C%20the%20German%20startup%20has%20designed%20a%20piece%20of%20hardware%20called%20a%20neuromorphic%20chip.%20These%20differ%20from%20traditional%20chips%2C%20which%20process%20information%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bstep-by-step%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Riegler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeuromorphic%20chips%20are%20built%20to%20work%20like%20a%20network%20of%20neurons%20(the%20brain's%20nerve%20cells)%2C%20which%20can%20handle%20multiple%20things%20at%20once%20and%20adapt%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThis%20makes%20them%20very%20good%20for%20tasks%20like%20pattern%20recognition%2C%20image%20processing%2C%20and%20sensory%20data%20analysis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Riegler%2C%20this%20makes%20it%20a%20faster%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20chips%20because%20it%20powers%20AI%20applications%20that%20need%20to%20run%20continuously%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20smart%20sensors%2C%20robots%2C%20or%20small%20devices%20%E2%80%94%20more%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECohere%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cohere%20cofounders%20Ivan%20Zhang%2C%20Nick%20Frosst%2C%20and%20Aidan%20Gomez.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6424a86ced593e00183f2a88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECohere%20cofounders%20Ivan%20Zhang%2C%20Nick%20Frosst%2C%20and%20Aidan%20Gomez.%3Cp%3ECohere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20raised%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%24975%20million%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThomvest%20Ventures%2C%20Index%20Ventures%2C%20Tiger%20Global%2C%20Radical%20Ventures%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuggested%20by%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUmesh%20Padval%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20Thomvest%20Ventures%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20does%20and%20why%20it's%20one%20to%20watch%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cohere%20is%20a%20foundational%20model%20layer%20company%20that%20provides%20large%20language%20models%20to%20enterprises%20so%20they%20can%20dev