ent%20and%20environmentally-friendly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rkanetkar%40insider.com%20(Riddhi%20Kanetkar)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-efficient-cheaper-greener-vcs-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infosys%20Mass%20Layoffs%20Leave%20Trainees%20Devastated%2C%20Internet%20Furious%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIT%20giant%20Infosys%20has%20laid%20off%20nearly%20700%20freshers%20from%20its%20Mysuru%20campus%2C%20the%20IT%20employees'%20union%20Nascent%20Information%20Technology%20Employees%20Senate%20(NITES)%20claimed%20on%20Friday.%20The%20union%20contended%20that%20the%20freshers%20were%20being%20terminated%20after%20just%20a%20few%20months%20of%20being%20onboarded%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20the%20Infosys%20mass%20terminations%20came%20as%20a%20devastating%20blow.%20Having%20waited%20over%20two%20years%20after%20graduation%20to%20start%20their%20careers%20at%20Infosys%20in%20September%202024%20finally%2C%20they%20now%20found%20themselves%20jobless%20just%20six%20months%20later.%20As%20they%20scrambled%20to%20book%20taxis%20and%20buses%20to%20return%20home%2C%20the%20harsh%20reality%20sank%20in-how%20would%20they%20break%20the%20news%20to%20their%20families%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20shocking%20and%20unethical%20move%2C%20Infosys%20has%20begun%20forcefully%20laying%20off%20around%20700%20campus%20recruits%20who%20were%20onboarded%20just%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Harpreet%20Singh%20Saluja%2C%20NITES%20president%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENITES%20alleged%20that%20the%20company%20also%20deployed%20%26quot%3Bbouncers%20and%20security%20personnel%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20termination%20process%20to%20intimidate%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20erupted%20with%20outrage%20as%20netizens%20shared%20their%20shock%20and%20sympathy%20for%20the%20affected%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%20on%20his%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20truly%20heartbreaking.%20These%20freshers%20waited%202-2.5%20years%20after%20receiving%20their%20offer%20letters%20from%20%23Infosys%20and%20finally%20joined%20in%20September%202024.%20Now%2C%20after%20just%20six%20months%2C%20nearly%20700%20of%20them%20have%20been%20laid%20off.%20Many%20might%20have%20turned%20down%20other%20opportunities%20for%20this-only%20to%20face%20this%20devastating%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20post%20described%20the%20scene%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20devastating%20photo%20in%20recent%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20highlighting%20the%20emotional%20toll%20on%20the%20young%20professionals%20who%20had%20placed%20their%20trust%20in%20one%20of%20India's%20largest%20IT%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20said%20on%20X%20that%20layoffs%20have%20a%20big%20negative%20impact%20on%20people's%20lives%2C%20saying%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BMany%20young%20college%20graduates%20and%20professionals%20will%20have%20to%20endure%20layoffs.%202025%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20tough%20economic%20year.%20Layoffs%20can%20have%20a%20big%20negative%20impact%20on%20people's%20lives%2C%20incomes%20and%20even%20marriages.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739271420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fguvg0hng_infosys-_625x300_01_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftruly-heartbreaking-infosys-mass-layoffs-leave-trainees-devastated-internet-furious-7685716%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Social%20media%20erupted%20with%20outrage%20as%20netizens%20shared%20their%20shock%20and%20sympathy%20for%20the%20affected%20employees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftruly-heartbreaking-infosys-mass-layoffs-leave-trainees-devastated-internet-furious-7685716%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAI's%20Most%20Feared%20Disruption%20Is%20Job%20Loss...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20On%20How%20To%20Tackle%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20addressed%20a%20global%20AI%20summit%20organised%20in%20Paris.%20He%20spoke%20extensively%20about%20how%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20is%20playing%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20daily%20lives%20of%20humans.%20While%20he%20advocated%20sharing%20the%20benefits%20of%20AI%20with%20all%2C%20especially%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20he%20cautioned%20about%20the%20biases%20in%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%20PM%20Modi%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20concern%20of%20job%20losses%20due%20to%20AI%20and%20highlighted%20how%20this%20must%20be%20tackled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20pull%20together%20our%20resources%20and%20talent%20and%20develop%20open%20source%20systems%20that%20enhance%20trust%20and%20transparency%20and%20develop%20quality%20datasets%2C%20free%20from%20biases%2C%20in%20order%20to%20benefit%20the%20world.%20AI%20must%20be%20about%20people-centric%20applications.%20We%20must%20address%20concerns%20related%20to%20cyber%20security%2C%20disinformation%2C%20and%20deep%20fakes%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20as%20leaders%20from%20across%20the%20world%20listened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20stressed%20on%20innovation%20and%20how%20%26quot%3BAI%20can%20help%20transform%20millions%20of%20lives%26quot%3B.%20This%20he%20said%20can%20be%20done%20in%20the%20fields%20of%20%26quot%3Bhealthcare%2C%20education%2C%20agriculture%2C%20and%20science.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20%26quot%3BAI%20can%20also%20help%20create%20a%20world%20in%20which%20the%20journey%20to%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20become%20easier%20and%20faster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20technology%20to%20be%20effective%20and%20useful%20for%20humankind%2C%20it%20must%20be%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20local%20ecosystems%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BAI's%20most-feared%20disruption%20is%20'loss%20of%20jobs'.%20But%20history%20has%20shown%20that%20work%20does%20not%20disappear%20due%20to%20technology.%26quot%3B%20He%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20nature%20of%20jobs%20change%20with%20time%2C%20and%20new%20types%20of%20jobs%20are%20created.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20noted%20that%20to%20address%20the%20concern%20of%20job%20losses%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20invest%20heavily%20on%20skilling%20and%20re-skilling%20of%20our%20people%20for%20an%20AI-driven%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20AI%20needs%20to%20be%20sustainable.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20high-energy%20intensity%20of%20AI%20needs%20to%20be%20scrutinised.%20This%20will%20require%20green%20power%20to%20fuel%20its%20future.%20India%20and%20France%20have%20formed%20the%20International%20Solar%20Alliance%20in%20order%20to%20harness%20the%20Sun%20to%20ensure%20there%20is%20plenty%20green%20energy%20supply%20for%20future%20technologies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConservation%20of%20energy%20is%20key%20for%20the%20future%20of%20AI%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20giving%20the%20example%20of%20a%20human%20brain.%20%26quot%3BA%20human%20brain%20can%20do%20everything%20from%20poetry%20to%20complex%20mathematics%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20energy%20needed%20even%20by%20an%20ordinary%20light%20bulb.%26quot%3B%20That%20is%20what%20the%20AI%20revolution%20must%20aim%20for%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDIAN%20ADVANCES%20IN%20AI%20TECH%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20AI%20revolution%20in%20India%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20successfully%20built%20a%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20for%20more%20than%201.4%20billion%20people%20at%20a%20very%20low%20cost.%26quot%3B%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20built%20around%20an%20open%20and%20accessible%20network.%20It%20has%20regulations%20and%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20applications%20in%20order%20to%20modernise%20our%20economy%2C%20reform%20governance%2C%20and%20transform%20the%20lives%20of%20our%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20digital%20commerce%20democratic%20and%20accessible%20to%20all.%20This%20vision%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20India's%20national%20AI%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20built%20an%20AI%20mission%20for%20good%2C%20and%20for%20all.%20Today%2C%20India%20leads%20in%20AI%20adaption%20and%20techno-legal%20solutions%20on%20data%20privacy.%20We%20are%20constantly%20developing%20AI%20applications%20for%20public%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20India's%20pragmatic%20approach%20to%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20in%20good%20governance%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20AI%20talent%20pools.%20We%20are%20also%20building%20our%20own%20large%20language%20model%20in%20AI%20keeping%20in%20mind%20our%20diversity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20also%20has%20a%20unique%20public-private%20partnership%20model%20for%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20willing%20to%20share%20its%20experience%20and%20expertise%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20is%20for%20everyone%20on%20the%20planet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20at%20the%20dawn%20of%20the%20AI%20age%20that%20will%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20humanity.%20Some%20people%20worry%20about%20machines%20becoming%20superior%20to%20human%20beings%20in%20terms%20of%20intelligence%2C%20but%20noone%20holds%20the%20key%20to%20our%20collective%20future%20and%20shared%20destiny%20other%20than%20all%20of%20us%20-%20humans.%20That%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20is%20what%20must%20guide%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20PM