d...%20As%20a%20member%20of%20standing%20committee%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%2C%20I%20will%20raise%20this%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20MPs%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20have%20submitted%20complaints%20against%20the%20podcaster.%20The%20Parliamentary%20panel%20on%20Information%20Technology%20is%20discussing%20whether%20to%20summon%20him.%20Allahbadia%20may%20be%20issued%20a%20notice%20and%20asked%20to%20appear%20and%20answer%20questions%20linked%20to%20the%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaising%20the%20matter%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Mr%20Mhaske%20said%20there%20is%20no%20censor%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20online%20platforms%20and%20content%20creators%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20this.%20%26quot%3BA%20specific%20norm%20should%20be%20framed%20against%20this.%20I%20am%20talking%20about%20this%20in%20the%20Parliament.%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20made%20wrong%20comments%20about%20mother%20and%20father.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20ruin%20our%20culture%20and%20tradition.%20In%20the%20name%20of%20democracy%2C%20they%20are%20making%20wrong%20remarks.%20There%20is%20no%20censor%20on%20OTT%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mhaske%20also%20flagged%20remarks%20about%20politicians%20on%20online%20platforms.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Centre%20must%20look%20into%20this.%20A%20Censor%20should%20be%20brought%20and%20strict%20rules%20framed%20for%20OTT%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Mhaske%2C%20MP%20from%20Maharashtra's%20Thane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllahbadia%2C%20who%20has%204.5%20million%20followers%20on%20Instagram%20and%201.05%20crore%20YouTube%20subscribers%2C%20now%20faces%20a%20police%20case%20for%20his%20remarks%20on%20India's%20Got%20Latent.%20Also%20known%20as%20the%20BeerBiceps%20Guy%2C%20he%20recently%20appeared%20in%20an%20episode%20of%20India's%20Got%20Latent%20hosted%20by%20comic%20Samay%20Raina.%20A%20short%20clip%20from%20the%20show%20shows%20Allahba