0have%20a%20job%20now%2C%20I'm%20aware%20that%20it's%20a%20very%20tough%20time%20for%20students%20looking%20for%20work.%20There%20are%20particular%20difficulties%20for%20international%20students%20who%20rely%20on%20companies%20to%20sponsor%20their%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1770fa4-fb02-4e35-a8ac-237fcbead998%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20kept%20getting%20ghosted%20or%20rejected%20for%20jobs.%20Being%20an%20international%20student%20made%20things%20even%20tougher.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20know%20exactly%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20after%20college%2C%20but%20growing%20up%2C%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20get%20into%20a%20company%20where%20I%20could%20use%20my%20tech%20skills%20to%20do%20something%20innovative%20with%20an%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20several%20internships%20while%20at%20university%20and%20also%20had%20an%20on-campus%20job%20helping%20students%20and%20faculty%20with%20tech%20problems.%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20my%20time%20at%20college%20to%20figure%20out%20my%20future%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%20my%20third%20year%2C%20I%20started%20applying%20for%20full-time%20jobs.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20employed%20by%20December%20so%20I%20could%20enjoy%20my%20last%20semester%20and%20the%20following%20summer%20without%20worrying%20about%20finding%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20an%20interest%20in%20entry-level%20sales%20engineer%20roles%20but%20wasn't%20having%20much%20success%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20sales%20experience.%20I%20pivoted%20toward%20quality%20engineering%20roles%20because%20I'd%20done%20an%20internship%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-seeker-applied-more-than-2000-roles-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapplied%20for%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20got%20ghosted%20or%20received%20automated%20rejection%20emails.%20I%20tried%20changing%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20templates%20and%20making%20YouTube%20videos%20to%20sell%20myself%20to%20recruiters%2C%20but%20nothing%20seemed%20to%20be%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20seemed%20to%20improve%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202023%20when%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fats-resume-how-to-build-templates-dream-job-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoptimizing%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20for%20ATS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20tracking%20software%20employers%20use%20to%20assess%20whether%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20matches%20the%20job%20description.%20I%20got%20ChatGPT%20premium%20and%20asked%20it%20to%20do%20an%20ATS%20analysis%20on%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20using%20the%20job%20descriptions%20for%20the%20roles%20I%20was%20applying%20to.%20I'd%20try%20to%20keep%20my%20score%20at%20about%2085%25%20because%20I%20thought%20this%20could%20help%20me%20avoid%20automated%20rejections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20for%20sure%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprompt-guide-chatgpt-job-hunting-personal-recruiter-careers-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20helped%2C%20but%20when%20I%20started%20using%20the%20tool%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20difference%20and%20received%20more%20callbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20faced%20another%20obstacle%20too.%20During%20the%20application%20process%20or%20interviews%20with%20recruiters%2C%20there%20would%20be%20a%20question%20about%20whether%20I'd%20need%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-companies-sponsor-h1b-visas-jpmorgan-goldman-sachs-blackrock-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evisa%20sponsorship%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20or%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20was%20a%20STEM%20student%2C%20I%20had%20access%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscis.gov%2Fworking-in-the-united-states%2Fstudents-and-exchange-visitors%2Foptional-practical-training-extension-for-stem-students-stem-opt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%