AmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcholera-outbreak-kills-more-than-100-in-angola-ministry%2Famp_articleshow%2F118144218.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcholera-outbreak-kills-more-than-100-in-angola-ministry%2Famp_articleshow%2F118144218.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20CCTVs%20At%20Mumbai%20Studio%20Didn't%20Capture%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia's%20Crass%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia's%20crass%20remarks%20at%20India's%20Most%20Latent%20roast%20show%20as%20the%20camera%20was%20covered%20with%20a%20black%20cloth%20before%20the%20shoot%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20Mumbai%20Police%20made%20the%20startling%20revelation%20after%20it%20started%20probing%20complaints%20linked%20to%20Allahbadia's%20remarks%20that%20have%20sparked%20a%20nationwide%20debate%20on%20mature%20content%20in%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20a%20police%20team%20today%20visited%20The%20Habitat%20cafe%20in%20Khar%20West%20where%20the%20episode%20was%20shot.%20This%20cafe%20serves%20as%20a%20key%20venue%20for%20comedy%20shows%20and%20is%20owned%20by%20Balraj%20Singh%20Ghai.%20Mr%20Ghai%20is%20a%20friend%20of%20comic%20Samay%20Raina%2C%20who%20hosts%20India's%20Got%20Latent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20asked%20The%20Habitat%20authorities%20for%20details%20about%20the%20controversial%20episode%20and%20its%20CCTV%20footage.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20they%20found%20that%20during%20most%20shoots%2C%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20are%20covered%20with%20a%20black%20cloth%20so%20they%20are%20not%20captured%20on%20CCTVs.%20Those%20who%20shoot%20these%20episodes%20take%20the%20content%20with%20them%20after%20the%20shooting.%20So%2C%20the%20studio%20does%20not%20have%20any%20record%20of%20what%20was%20shot.%20C