not%20going%20to%20give%20any%20context%20or%20justification%20or%20reasoning%20behind%20whatever%20happened.%20I%20am%20just%20here%20for%20an%20apology.%20I%20personally%20had%20a%20lapse%20in%20judgement.%20It%20wasn't%20cool%20on%20my%20part%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739268660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fdh0liip8_ranveer-allahbadia-samay-raina_625x300_10_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franveer-allahbadia-beer-biceps-indias-got-latent-why-cctvs-at-mumbai-studio-didnt-capture-ranveer-allahbadias-crass-remark-7685387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20no%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia's%20crass%20remarks%20at%20India's%20Most%20Latent%20roast%20show%20as%20the%20camera%20was%20covered%20with%20a%20black%20cloth%20before%20the%20shoot%2C%20sources%20have%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franveer-allahbadia-beer-biceps-indias-got-latent-why-cctvs-at-mumbai-studio-didnt-capture-ranveer-allahbadias-crass-remark-7685387%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Surrey%20confirms%20deal%20with%20Reliance%2C%20keeps%2051%25%20stake%20in%20Oval%20Invincibles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739268599000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsurrey-confirms-deal-with-reliance-keeps-51-stake-in-oval-invincibles-125021101105_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reliance%20Industries%20Limited%20(RIL)%20owners%20of%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20through%20its%20subsidiary%2C%20RISE%20Worldwide%2C%20bought%2049%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20The%20Hundred%20team%20for%2060m%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsurrey-confirms-deal-with-reliance-kee