20closer%20to%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%2010%20years%2C%20I%20spent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupercommuter-travels-7-hours-get-work-productive-journey-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%20four%20hours%20a%20day%20commuting%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20London%20for%20work.%20I%20still%20do%20the%20commute%20a%20few%20days%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20worth%20it%20to%20improve%20my%20family's%20quality%20of%20life%20while%20maintaining%20a%20London%20job%20with%20a%20London%20salary%2C%20but%20if%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20do%20so%20again%2C%20I'd%20ask%20for%20more%20flexibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22342987f2-6af9-4766-81f5-883392b29ac4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20countryside%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222856%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20backyard%20of%20a%20home%20in%20the%20English%20countryside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67aa48287bb3f854015c623f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222142%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDearden's%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anna-Louise%20Dearden%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20original%20reason%20for%20the%20move%20was%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20family%2C%20I%20loved%20Wellingborough's%20slow%2C%20outdoorsy%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20I%20bought%20a%20five-bedroom%20Victorian%20home%20for%20%C2%A3285%2C000.%20If%20I%20had%20purchased%20a%20similar%20home%20in%20London%20at%20the%20time%2C%20it%20would've%20been%20close%20to%20%C2%A31%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20have%20a%20100-ft%20yard%2C%20which%20I'd%20never%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc1f4a1e-a83a-4b8a-8335-e1dc320d6db0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20commute%20was%20140%20miles%20round%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20day%20began%20with%20a%2020-minute%20walk%20from%20my%20home%20to%20the%20tr