%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupercommuter-travels-4-states-get-work-earns-6-figures-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etried%20supercommuting%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20opted%20for%20a%20local%20job%2C%20as%20trains%20and%20childcare%20in%20the%20UK%20are%20so%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fca865ef-33bf-4156-8d24-3c114bcdc8cf%5C%22%3EDelays%20can%20also%20be%20a%20day-ruiner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20not%20uncommon%20to%20encounter%20bumps%20in%20the%20road.%20Even%20short%20delays%20or%20scheduled%20maintenance%20can%20disrupt%20plans%20and%20make%20the%20trip%20unpleasant%2C%20but%20it%20comes%20with%20the%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20wasn't%20home%20all%20the%20time%20and%20missed%20a%20couple%20of%20school%20events%2C%20I%20have%20no%20regrets.%20I%20attended%20most%20important%20events%20and%20sports%20matches%2C%20and%20my%20kids%20were%20very%20well-socialized%20and%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c0e827d-7628-4379-8c99-1a55ae3b4561%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnce%20I%20became%20a%20freelancer%2C%20my%20daily%20commute%20ended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20made%20redundant%20in%202010%20and%20decided%20to%20leave%20my%20in-house%20editor%20career%20to%20provide%20freelance%20public%20relations%20and%20journalism%20services.%20Now%2C%20I%20only%20need%20to%20commute%20to%20London%20for%20the%20occasional%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20are%20grown%20and%20have%20moved%20out%2C%20but%20Stella%2C%20my%20Bernese%20Mountain%20Dog-Labrador%20mix%2C%20and%20I%20enjoy%20walking%20through%20the%20woods%20and%20experiencing%20everything%20the%20countryside%20offers.%20Stella%20prefers%20that%20I%20limit%20my%20commuting%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20I'm%20happy%20to%20oblige.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ef76280-1593-427a-8f70-b60ec2108edb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20would%20happily%20supercommute%20again%2C%20but%20only%20part%20time%3C%2