rk%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Altman's%20vision%20of%20the%20future%2C%20AI%20is%20so%20far%20advanced%20that%20everyone%20has%20access%20to%20the%20equivalent%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20competent%20company%20on%20Earth.%26quot%3B%20To%20compete%20in%20that%20cutting-edge%20world%2C%20Altman%20recommended%20the%20students%20in%20attendance%20develop%20new%20skills%20to%20help%20them%20leverage%20AI%20to%20their%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20skills%20that%20you%20need%20in%20that%20world%20are%20figuring%20out%20what%20people%20want%2C%20sort%20of%20creative%20vision%2C%20quick%20adaptability%2C%20resilience%20as%20everything%20is%20changing%20around%20you%2C%20and%20the%20sort%20of%20learning%20how%20to%20work%20with%20these%20tools%20to%20do%20way%20more%20than%20people%20could%20without%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20students%20do%20enter%20the%20workforce%2C%20Weil%20said%20they%20could%20benefit%20from%20keeping%20AI%20in%20mind.%20The%20best-positioned%20companies%20are%20those%20that%20see%20the%20technology%20as%20a%20potential%20boost%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20competitor%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20building%20something%2C%20and%20you're%20nervous%20about%20our%20next%20model%20release%20because%20it%20might%20be%20able%20to%20do%20the%20thing%20that%20you're%20doing%2C%20that's%20not%20a%20good%20place%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Weil%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you're%20building%20something%20and%20you%20can't%20wait%20for%20our%20next%20model%20release%2C%20because%20you're%20just%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20capabilities%20and%20our%20next%20model%20release%20that'll%20be%20that%20much%20smarter%20is%20going%20to%20make%20your%20product%20amazing%2C%20that's%20a%20good%20place%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20which%20generates%20revenue%20from%20selling%20access%20to%20its%20AI%20models%20to%20companies%20as%20well%20as%20consumers%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%