incompetent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20losing%20the%20Delhi%20elections%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20called%20a%20meeting%20of%20Punjab%20MLAs%20in%20Delhi.%20Reports%20suggest%20that%20he%20is%20trying%20to%20remove%C2%A0%40BhagwantMann%20Ji%20from%20the%20CM%20post%20by%20branding%20him%20as%20incompetent.%20He%20failed%20to%20fulfill%20his%20promise%20of%20giving%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20women%2C%20was%20unsuccessful%20in%20curbing%20drug%20abuse%20and%20has%20worsened%20Punjab's%20situation.%20Now%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20put%20all%20failure%20on%20Bhagwant%20Mann.%20He%20is%20making%20AAP%20Punjab%20MLAs%20say%20that%20Kejriwal%20is%20a%20'good%20man'%20and%20should%20be%20made%20Chief%20Minister%20instead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Mann%20was%20asked%20about%20this%20claim%2C%20he%20smiled%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20them%20say%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20assured%20that%20the%20Punjab%20government%20would%20fulfill%20its%20promise%20of%20giving%20Rs%201%2C000%20every%20month%20to%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20responded%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Partap%20Singh%20Bajwa's%20claim%20that%20more%20than%2020%20AAP%20MLAs%20in%20Punjab%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20him.%20%26quot%3BPartap%20Bajwa%20has%20been%20saying%20this%20for%20nearly%20three%20years.%20Ask%20him%20to%20count%20the%20number%20of%20(Congress)%20MLAs%20in%20Delhi%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20mocking%20the%20Congress%20for%20its%20hat-trick%20of%20scoring%20zero%20seats%20in%20the%20Delhi%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20Mr%20Bajwa's%20claims%20that%20he%20may%20quit%20AAP.%20%26quot%3BLet%20them%20talk.%20We%20have%20built%20this%20party%20with%20our%20blood%20and%20sweat.%20Actually%2C%20they%20have%20a%20culture%20of%20switching%20sides...%C2%A0One%20of%20their%20leaders%20was%20beating%20a%20dhol%20to%20celebrate%20AAP's%20defeat.%20Someone%20asked%20hi