0Medicaid%20Services%20in%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration.%20Lindemann%20worked%20at%20Russell%20Street%20Ventures%20as%20a%20venture%20associate%2C%20an%20entry-level%20job%20in%20the%20venture%20capital%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindemann%2C%20Davis%2C%20McKinsey%2C%20and%20Russell%20Street%20Ventures%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20campaign%20finance%20records%2C%20the%20White%20House%20DOGE%20staffer%20Ramada%20is%20a%20Miami%20venture%20capitalist%20who%20donated%20more%20than%20%241%2C000%20to%20Republican%20fundraising%20committees%20last%20year.%20One%20of%20his%20companies%2C%20Spring%20Tide%20Capital%2C%20invested%20in%20Impulse%20Space%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20by%20a%20SpaceX%20employee%20and%20has%20contracted%20with%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamada%20and%20Spring%20Tide%20Capital%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20comment%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fcb2ea30-2589-498c-bb28-f40f23466fee%5C%22%3ELaw%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20lawyers%20listed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20DOGE%20White%20House%20staff%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20have%20clerked%20for%20conservative%20Supreme%20Court%20justices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaynor%2C%20a%20graduate%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia's%20law%20school%2C%20clerked%20for%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20term%20that%20started%20in%20October%202016%20and%20spent%20time%20as%20an%20associate%20at%20Sullivan%20%26amp%3B%20Cromwell.%20During%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20he%20served%20as%20an%20assistant%20to%20the%20solicitor%20general.%20He%20has%20argued%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20at%20least%20eight%20times.%20He%20was%20most%20recently%20a%20senior%20attorney%20and%20special%20counsel%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20practice%20at%20the%20Pacific%20Legal%20Foundation%2C%20a%20libertarian%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaynor's%20November%20TV%20segment%20and%20Trump's%20executive%20order%2