e%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaims%20the%20ghee%20used%20to%20make%20the%20world-famous%20Tirupati%20laddoo%20contained%20animal%20fat%20made%20headlines%20last%20year%2C%20reaching%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20sparking%20a%20religious%20and%20political%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20noted%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkeep-gods-out-of-politics-supreme-court-on-tirupati-laddoo-row-6682442%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereligion%20and%20politics%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20mix%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20ordered%20the%20federal%20agency%20to%20fully%20investigate%2C%20with%20help%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Police%20and%20a%20senior%20official%20from%20the%20central%20government-run%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India%2C%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remand%20report%20submitted%20by%20that%20team%20this%20week%20outlines%20several%20instances%20in%20which%20one%20or%20more%20of%20the%20four%20dairies%20mentioned%20manipulated%20documents%20and%20prices%20to%20win%20tenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20example%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20was%20AR%20Dairy%20claiming%20to%20be%20able%20to%20supply%20at%20least%20six%20tonnes%20of%20cow%20milk%20fat%20per%20day%20from%20dairies%20within%201%2C500%20km%20of%20Tirupati%2C%20as%20required%20by%20the%20tender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20special%20team%2C%20or%20SIT%2C%20found%20this%20claim%20to%20be%20false%2C%20and%20that%20AR%20Dairy%20had%20%26quot%3Bsubmitted%20false%20and%20fabricated%20documents...%20in%20collusion%20and%20conspiracy%20with%20others%26quot%3B%20to%20alter%20butter%2C%20ghee%2C%20and%20milk%20production%20figures%20for%20earlier%20years%20to%20show%20they%20could%20meet%20future%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIT%20claimed%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20actual%20procurement%20of%20cow%20milk%20fat%20handling%20per%20annum%20for%20AR%20Dairy%2C%20as%20per%20FSSAI%20rep