m-donald-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F118139053.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NZ%20Star%20Rachin%20Ravindra%2C%20Injured%20In%20Lahore%20Stadium%2C%20Blamed%20For%20Own%20Injury%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20injury%20to%20New%20Zealand%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rachin%20Ravindra%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F113659-rachin-ravindra-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERachin%20Ravindra%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20an%20ODI%20match%20against%20Pakistan%20at%20Lahore's%20Gaddafi%20Stadium%20became%20a%20huge%20talking%20point%20ahead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20In%20a%20rather%20bizarre%20and%20worrying%20incident%2C%20Rachin%20failed%20to%20spot%20the%20ball%20in%20the%20glare%20of%20the%20floodlights%20at%20the%20venue%20and%20ended%20up%20incurring%20a%20serious%20injury%20that%20left%20him%20bloodied%20on%20the%20field.%20While%20some%20big%20names%20in%20Pakistan's%20cricketing%20fraternity%20admitted%20that%20the%20LED%20lights%20at%20the%20venue%20seem%20to%20be%20causing%20some%20issue%2C%20others%20have%20refused%20to%20make%20corrections.%20Instead%2C%20they've%20blamed%20Rachin%20for%20the%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Pakistan%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Salman%20Butt%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F592-salman-butt-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESalman%20Butt%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20those%20who%20brushed%20aside%20the%20criticism%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20has%20been%20getting%20since%20the%20incident.%20He%20also%20feels%20the%20talks%20around%20the%20ICC%20event%20to%20be%20shifted%20to%20another%20country%20are%20also%20ridiculous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20point%20trying%20to%20make%20people%20understand%20when%20they%20don't%20want%20to.%20It's%20irrelevant.%20These%20are%20some%20of%20the%20latest%20LED%20lights%20that%20have%20been%20installed%2C%20so%20these%20are%20fine.%20When%20New%20Zealand%20players%20hit%20sixes%20off%20deliveries%20bowled%20at%20close%20to%20150%20kph%2C%20were%20the%20lights%20not%20working%20then%3F%20A%20player%20who%20was%20standing%2070%20meters%20away%20failed%20to%20take%20the%20catch%20because%20of%20his%20misjudgment.%20He%20is%20a%20fine%20fielder%2C%20but%20perhaps%20his%20leg%20slipped%2C%20and%20he%20got%20hurt%2C%26quot%3B%20Butt%20said%20on%20a%20local%20news%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Pakistan%20news%20anchor%20also%20maintained%20a%20similar%20stance%2C%20while%20also%20highlighting%20the%20floodlight%20failure%20that%20happened%20during%20the%20India%20vs%20England%20ODI%20match%2C%20bringing%20the%20match%20to%20a%20halt%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20some%20of%20the%20prior%20campaigns%20that%20stated%20Pakistan%20cannot%20host%20a%20tournament%20as%20big%20as%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20because%20the%20stadiums%20are%20not%20ready%2C%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20the%20same%20people%2C%20'What%20do%20you%20have%20to%20say%20about%20what%20happened%20in%20Barabati%20Stadium%3F%20That%20is%20an%20established%20stadium.'%20So%2C%20I%20want%20to%20say%20that%20these%20things%20happen.%20These%20are%20not%20big%20issues.%20Just%20because%20Rachin%20was%20hit%20in%20the%20face%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20PCB%20is%20to%20be%20blamed%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%2C%20however%2C%20who%20do%20feel%20that%20the%20PCB%20isn't%20in%20a%20state%20to%20host%20tournaments%20of%20the%20stature%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20even%20have%20the%20money.%20Whatever%20is%20done%20to%20maintain%20the%20stadiums%20comes%20from%20state%20associations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20former%20Pakistan%20cricketer%20Tanvir%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20great%20Hanif%20Mohammad's%20son%20Shoaib%20highlighted%20an%20intriguing%20point%2C%20suggesting%20even%20New%20Zealand%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Daryl%20Mitchell%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F50709-daryl-joseph-mitchell-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDaryl%20Mitchell%3C%2Fa%3E%20hinted%20at%20some%20problem%20with%20the%20floodlight%20at%20the%20Gaddafi%20stadium%20before%20Rachin%20was%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20definitely.%20In%20fact%2C%20before%20the%20whole%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20incident%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20even%20Daryl%20Mitchell%20had%20some%20trouble%20spotting%20the%20ball%20when%20he%20fielding.%20The%20moment%20he%20took%20the%20catch%2C%20at%20a%20normal%20height%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20his%20expressions%20indicated%20that%20he%20couldn't%20quite%20see%20the%20ball%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20if%20he%20too%20faced%20the%20same%20problem%2C%20something%20is%20wrong.%20The%20placement%20of%20the%20floodlights%20is%20a%20technical%20aspect.%20Rachin%20was%20standing%20at%20deep%20square%20leg%2C%20and%20the%20light%20was%20right%20before%20him.%20Now%2C%20that%20is%20not%20usually%20where%20floodlights%20are%20erected%20in%20a%20stadium.%20There%20is%20some%20glare%20due%20to%20which%20the%20ball%20is%20getting%20lost%20in%20the%20players'%20vision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739258460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fil6pog1_rachin-ravindra-afp_625x300_09_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-puts-blame-back-on-rachin-ravindra-over-nasty-head-injury-despite-floodlights-issue-7683652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20Zealand%20cricketer%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20incurred%20a%20nasty%20head%20injury%20during%20an%20ODI%20match%20against%20Pakistan%20at%20the%20Gaddafi%20Stadium%20in%20Lahore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A87%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sidharth%20and%20Janhvi%20SPOTTED%20on%20'Param%20Sundari'%20sets%22%2C%22conte