%20diseases%20in%20India%20and%20policy%20shifts%20needed%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%20is%20commendable%20that%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20passing%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20dimmed%20Prasanna%E2%80%99s%20mission%20and%20vision%20in%20the%20slightest.%20In%20a%20world%20where%20everyone%20is%20for%20themselves%2C%20we%20have%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20paradox.%20He%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20started%20this%20journey%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20ensuring%20my%20daughter%20received%20funding%20for%20her%20treatment%2C%20it%20probably%20would%20have%20ceased.%20But%20I%20started%20it%20to%20help%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F108289%2Fliving-with-a-chronic-illness-affordable-healthcare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20with%20rare%20diseases%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20worried%20parents%20with%20no%20one%20to%20turn%20to%20for%20the%20answers.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20and%20continuing%20hope%3A%20The%20Organization%20for%20Rare%20Diseases%20India%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20the%20nature%20of%20Prasanna%E2%80%99s%20schedule%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20lucky%20to%20secure%20an%20interview%20with%20him.%20His%20time%20is%20a%20juggle%20between%20the%20operations%20of%20ORDI%20and%20taking%20India%E2%80%99s%20rare%20disease%20advocacy%20to%20a%20global%20stage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20saw%20Prasanna%20attend%20an%20APARDO%20(Asia%20Pacific%20Alliance%20of%20Rare%20Disease%20Organisations)%20meeting%20in%20Manila%2C%20Philippines%2C%20where%20he%20discussed%20the%20latest%20developments%20of%20rare%20diseases%20in%20India%3B%20meet%20with%20Dr%20Jan%20Klat%20of%20Merck%20Healthcare%20to%20discuss%20potential%20clinical%20trials%20that%20Indian%20patients%20could%20be%20a%20part%20of%3B%20and%20represent%20India%20at%20COLLABORATE%20Initiative%20at%20Prague%2C%20Czech%20Re