aption%5C%22%3EPrasanna%20Shirol%20was%20instrumental%20in%20setting%20up%20the%20Rare%20Diseases%20Care%20Coordination%20Centre%20(RDCCC)%20at%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Institute%20of%20Child%20Health%20in%20Bengaluru%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20gratitude%20for%20this%20schedule%20lights%20up%20his%20face%20as%20he%20tells%20me%20about%20it.%20A%20decade%20ago%2C%20his%20life%20was%20very%20different.%20Prasanna%20had%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20start%20ORDI%2C%20he%20was%20spending%20a%20lakh%20and%20a%20half%20every%20month%20to%20finance%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20treatment%2C%20and%20he%20was%20very%20close%20to%20losing%20hope.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20I%20managed%20to%20run%20my%20home%20for%20those%2012%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20But%20the%20kindness%20of%20the%20world%20kept%20him%20going%2C%20and%20today%2C%20through%20ORDI%2C%20he%20is%20attempting%20to%20be%20that%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20a%20parent%20who%20needs%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20clinch%20the%20argument%20that%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20cure%20for%20rare%20diseases%2C%20Prasanna%20has%20a%20counter-rhetoric%3A%20%E2%80%9CGive%20them%20relief%20then.%E2%80%9D%20Through%20their%20work%2C%20ORDI%20is%20challenging%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20journey%20with%20rare%20diseases%20is%20a%20fight%20to%20be%20won.%20Instead%2C%20they%20emphasise%20making%20the%20battle%20less%20painful.%20One%20of%20their%20most%20significant%20strides%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F162706%2Fbengaluru-pil-supreme-court-rare-disease-father-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eensuring%20access%20to%20court-approved%20medical%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20children%20with%20rare%20diseases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%