%20retired%20in%202020%20after%20a%20distinguished%20career%2C%20including%20serving%20as%20the%20Secretary%20of%20Agriculture%20for%20Punjab.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20aquifers%20is%20depleting%20at%20an%20unsustainable%20rate%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20paddy%20cultivation%2C%20which%20isn%E2%80%99t%20even%20native%20to%20the%20area.%20The%20data%20and%20observations%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades%20were%20alarming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20crisis%20pushed%20him%20to%20act.%20Rather%20than%20simply%20watch%20as%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20most%20vital%20resource%20continued%20to%20decline%2C%20Kahan%20Singh%20focused%20on%20creating%20a%20solution%20to%20sustain%20agriculture%20while%20preserving%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20groundwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20strong%20academic%20background%20in%20agriculture%20and%20decades%20of%20field%20experience%2C%20the%2064-year-old%20developed%20what%20he%20calls%20the%20SRB%20technique%20%E2%80%94%20Seeding%20of%20Rice%20on%20Beds.%20This%20method%20significantly%20reduces%20the%20water%20needed%20for%20paddy%20farming%2C%20saving%20up%20to%2075%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTraditionally%2C%20paddy%20cultivation%20requires%20vast%20amounts%20of%20standing%20water%2C%20often%20using%20up%20to%204%2C000%20litres%20for%20producing%20one%20kilogram%20of%20rice.%20Fields%20are%20flooded%20throughout%20the%20growing%20season%20to%20suppress%20weed%20growth%2C%20a%20practice%20that%20inadvertently%20drains%20the%20water%20table%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20game-changer%20for%20water%20conservation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20his%20networ